				<td colspan="2"><span>I can't seem to find some answers I am looking for so I'll start here.
<br />

<br />
1. What does the mod number on an instrument/armor/weapon actually stand for?
<br />

<br />
2. Is a weapon/armor with a &quot;brass 2.0&quot; the same as a instrument with &quot;brass 2.0&quot;?
<br />

<br />
3. What is the first level that a Bard can kite multiple mobs. It appears at lvl 2 we get an aoe DD.
<br />

<br />
I think thats good for starters<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /> Thanks in advance for any help.
<br />

<br />
PS Not a noob, but a Bard noob, so normal terms make sense to me<img src="/skins/default/images/emotions/emotion-1.gif" border="0" alt="Smiley" hspace="2" /></span></td>
